What you need to know:

Philadelphia are looking to earn the top seed and home court advantage in the postseason.The 76ers improved to 38-17 on the season, just one game ahead of Brooklyn at 37-18.Embiid also shot 13-of-29 from the floor and pulled down 13 rebounds as the 76ers saw their 22-point lead slashed to just three in the fourth.Kyrie Irving led the Nets with 37 points.